{"tid":1756851,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【公投】12.1 舉行九區同步遊行！誠邀曾經舉辦地區遊行搞手入紙申請！","createTime":"2019-11-26T08:31:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T09:05:05.000Z","uid":167548,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"15352fc37dd097c92a5b6c0c1d79216db65b4974","tid":1756851,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:31:23.000Z","msg":"呢個有沒得諗？<br />\n有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n沒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n背景：12月8日先有民陣大遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;但是地點是要過海<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;兩星期後中共倘授權班狗狗發狗癲就仆硬街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;不如趁民意高企, 柒婆火水救火時, 再加人權法未簽前夕, 盡快嚟次大遊行啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;今日唔知聽日事成十日變化好大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>11.23 反解放軍聯合陣線！「逢九必亂」！九陣遊行！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1727481\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1727481</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n轉做星期日12月1日九區同步遊行？<br />\n因為12月8日有民陣舉辦大型集會，<br />\n但是嗰情況就好似攬炒集會咁,<br />\n沒不反, 打大交, 大量被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><br />\n人口分佈<br />\n新界:九龍:港島 ~<span style=\"color: red;\"> 4:2:1</span><br />\n<blockquote><br />\n規劃署今日（六月八日）發表載列2018年至2026年香港人口分布最新推算數字的「人口分布推算2018－2026」報告書。推算新界及九龍的人口，在2016年至2026年期間，會分別增加441600人及140200人，在2026年其人口會分別達到428萬人及238萬人，而同期間香港島的人口，則由125萬逐漸減少至116萬。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">新界</span></strong><br />\n1. 屯門  (參考過往遊行)<br />\n2. 沙田  (參考過往遊行)<br />\n3. 大埔  (參考過往遊行) <br />\n4. 上水  (參考過往遊行)<br />\n5. 荃葵青  (參考過往遊行)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">九龍</span></strong><br />\n6. 油尖旺  (參考過往遊行)<br />\n<del>7. 黃大仙</del><span style=\"color: red;\"> (可以拼合埋觀塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />達成九之數, 咒死中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)</span><br />\n8. 觀塘 (參考過往遊行)<br />\n9. TKO  (參考過往遊行)<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">港島</span></strong><br />\n10. 港島  (參考過往遊行)<br />\n<br />\n[破局] 令藍絲老解收皮、黑警精神更崩潰，搞多次超多人既大型活動就得<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1727350\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1727350</a><br />\n<br />\nBtw 終於明點解港島不利港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抄班神鬼風水撚口吻講<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">九</span></strong><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">龍</span></strong>克撚死中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">九</span></strong>代表亂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>龍</strong></span>代表天命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">11.23 反解放軍聯合陣線！「逢九必亂」！九陣遊行！</span></span></strong><br />\n有冇得諗？下星期六11月23日搞遊行, 呢九個區包納曬<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>港九新界</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><br />\n有得諗, 照舊遊行路線, 落街就示威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇得諗, 班POPO唔會比你地和平集結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n推到民陣申請<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫手推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"8758817fc536a69805f529464714024483b4cd25","tid":1756851,"uid":167548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:32:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EZk4Ekg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEZk4Ekg.jpg&h=1e89f6b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n突發 今個星期四有野要做！全世界入嚟！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/eAJvAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/eAJvAS</a>"},{"pid":"1b49e0b69532ca4de65727cc5669fd104858d6b2","tid":1756851,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:33:13.000Z","msg":"將兩百萬人分散去九區諗唔諗得過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&nbsp;<br />\n前提是要曾經舉辦地區遊行搞手入紙申請！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40d3a2cccb7a1391a87b6a65edd1428fa66f2245","tid":1756851,"uid":124134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:34:27.000Z","msg":"【必入】Reactivate場運動致勝formula，推到岑子杰入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1756604\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1756604</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"439a0ad240f0d71e72fc6e7d7f190e891f9b6a9a","tid":1756851,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:34:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"190aa2c9f7459e00838ee6f282301988642fd54c","tid":1756851,"uid":277235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:35:50.000Z","msg":"贊成<br />\n吹話區議會謝票遊行囉，就算嘉年華少少都冇所謂，最緊要ｋｅｅｐ住團火<br />\n喺曬咁多區，啲離地少數派冇得扮睇唔到<br />\n激撚死佢地"},{"pid":"73ea68e7eb717a9c1e7372ac1dda852e0e62fd10","tid":1756851,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"190aa2c9f7459e00838ee6f282301988642fd54c","tid":1756851,"uid":277235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:35:50.000Z","msg":"贊成<br />\n吹話區議會謝票遊行囉，就算嘉年華少少都冇所謂，最緊要ｋｅｅｐ住團火<br />\n喺曬咁多區，啲離地少數派冇得扮睇唔到<br />\n激撚死佢地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:36:49.000Z","msg":"推起去啦 今日星期二 聽日入紙 今個星期日冇活動啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22ee4b97a74bdea251f82570e5457ff3ee3d673b","tid":1756851,"uid":167548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T08:37:47.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins><span style=\"color: red;\">